query:
SELECT
                    COUNT(*) AS "count!",
                    circuit_id AS "circuit_id!",
                    aggregation_round AS "aggregation_round!",
                    status AS "status!",
                    protocol_version AS "protocol_version!"
                FROM
                    prover_jobs_fri
                WHERE
                    status = 'queued'
                    OR status = 'in_progress'
                GROUP BY
                    circuit_id,
                    aggregation_round,
                    status,
                    protocol_version
